=== Tiny Planet ===
1. '''''It's a Small World''''', gives {{reward|phy|rsh1|empty|empty}}, proceed to '''''Lunar Impact'''''

2. '''''Lunar Impact''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}, proceed to '''''A Small Problem'''''

3. '''''A Small Problem''''', gives {{reward|soc|rsh2|empty|empty}}

* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Establish contact."'', available IF NOT homicidal or barbaric despoilers, proceed to '''''Communications Established'''''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 3 ''"Observe passively."'', available IF NOT homicidal or barbaric despoilers, outcome '''''Observed From Afar,'' ends the rift'''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Demand ransom."'', available IF barbaric despoilers, proceed to '''''Communications Established'''''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Inform them that their doom has come."'', available IF homicidal,  proceed to '''''Communications''''' '''''Established'''''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 3 ''"Watch the destruction unfold."'', available iIFhomicidal or barbaric despoilers, outcome '''''Observed From Afar'', ends the rift'''

4. '''''Communications Established''''', gives {{reward|ast|ast1|empty|empty}}

* {{icon|astral rift difficulty hard}} 6 ''"Attempt to fix the moon's orbit."'', available IF NOT homicidal or barbaric despoilers, proceed to '''''Back in Orbit'''''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 3 ''"Destroy the moon."'', available IF NOT a Pacifist Xenophile, proceed to '''''No More Moon'''''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 1 ''"Cut communications. Observe passively."'', available IF NOT homicidal or barbaric despoilers, outcome '''''Observed From Afar,'' ends the rift'''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 1 ''"Cut communications. Watch the destruction unfold."'', available IF homicidal or barbaric despoilers, gives {{reward|uni|rsh3|empty|empty}} IF homicidal, outcome '''''Observed From Afar,'' ends the rift'''

5a. '''''Back in Orbit''''', gives {{reward|phy|rsh3|empty|empty}}, outcome '''''Tidal Locking Breakthrough, ends the rift'''''

5b. '''''No More Moon''''', gives 5 {{iconify|Minerals}}, {{reward|phy|rsh1|empty|empty}}, IF homicidal or barbaric despoilers also gives {{reward|uni|rsh3|empty|empty}}, outcome '''''Model Planet,'' ends the rift'''

* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 1 ''"Put them out of their misery."'', outcome '''''Shallow Impact,'' ends the rift'''
* {{icon|astral rift difficulty easy}} 3 ''"Deploy remote research devices."'', outcome '''''Model Planet,'' ends the rift'''

